title: What are some real pictures that prove aliens exist? - Quora

response.answer_text: Yep, as Bent said, there are no credible picture or anything else for that mater of alien visitors ever. never will be as the distance to the next planet with an intelligent species that may be out there somewhere is far too great to overcome. Sad but true
